comments.content: related bug is https://bugs.launchpad.net/nova/+bug/1239709, so please update your openstack to at least 2013.2.1 .
comments.author: https://api.launchpad.net/1.0/~heut2008

comments.content: is 2013.2.1 backwards compatible with the earlier release?  our existing cluster all run 2013.2-0 so my main concern is if this would impact my existing cluster install.
